# WKBackgroundFetchResult.noData

**Case**

The notification has no associated content.

## Declaration

```swift
case noData
```

## Fetch Results

- **WKBackgroundFetchResult.failed**: The download attempt failed.
- **WKBackgroundFetchResult.newData**: The download attempt succeeded.
